overview: Hot, dirty and fascinatingly wicked, Chi Chi LaRue again takes us on a trip through her depraved fantasies. Shameless and with a seething fire in their eyes we encounter LaRues models, both well-known faces and new talent. The smell of leather, steamy settings, sweaty lovers and powerful machinery create an irresistibly thrilling masculine mood. We dare you to try and escape!
tagline: One of the most appealing things about Link is that from jocks to daddies, there is something for everyone - with just the right amount of kink.
title: Link 5: The Evolution
